WEBVTT

00:03.342 --> 00:07.487
Previously, on The Truth About
the Harry Quebert Affair...

00:11.023 --> 00:12.902
In America,
ladies and gentlemen,

00:12.904 --> 00:15.475
we are obsessed
with sex and morality.

00:15.477 --> 00:16.818
Excuse me, why, uh...

00:16.820 --> 00:18.854
why are blowjobs bad?

00:18.856 --> 00:20.275
I'm just, personally,
I'm a big fan, I don't know...

00:21.429 --> 00:23.346
You're the reason
I'm here, Professor.

00:23.348 --> 00:25.305
You're what I aspire to be, sir.

00:25.307 --> 00:28.108
Well, Mr. Goldman,
I have no doubt

00:28.110 --> 00:30.182
that you're going to be
a huge success.

00:34.369 --> 00:35.673
I'm totally blocked, Harry.

00:35.675 --> 00:36.633
It's been over a year,

00:36.635 --> 00:38.054
<i>and I got nothing.</i>

00:38.056 --> 00:39.360
You know,
why don't you come to me?

00:39.362 --> 00:40.435
You made it!

00:40.437 --> 00:41.280
- How are you, man?
- Ah, good to see you!

00:48.846 --> 00:50.573
What, are you
spying on me, Marcus?

00:50.575 --> 00:53.567
This needs to stay between us.

00:53.569 --> 00:55.717
<i>Author Harry Quebert
was arrested today</i>

00:55.719 --> 00:57.446
<i>after police
discovered the body</i>

00:57.448 --> 01:00.633
<i>of 15-year-old Nola Kellergan,</i>

01:00.635 --> 01:03.436
<i>who disappeared from her house
in August of 1975.</i>

01:03.438 --> 01:04.819
How's it looking for him?

01:04.821 --> 01:06.047
Not good.

01:06.049 --> 01:08.812
They found a manuscript
of his "Origin of Evil"

01:08.814 --> 01:10.579
buried with
the dead girl.

01:10.581 --> 01:12.076
Talk to
the nice townsfolk.

01:12.078 --> 01:14.227
Those hicks are
potential witnesses.

01:14.229 --> 01:16.300
Hey, we're gonna get
you out of here, okay?

01:16.302 --> 01:18.374
Is there anything
you haven't told me?

01:18.376 --> 01:19.949
I was supposed
to meet Nola at 8:00.

01:19.951 --> 01:22.559
<i>That was the night
she disappeared.</i>

01:22.561 --> 01:24.288
It's a fucking
disaster!

01:24.290 --> 01:25.747
If the prosecution
gets hold of this,

01:25.749 --> 01:27.669
Harry is screwed.

01:28.706 --> 01:31.238
<i>"On my desk,
there's a porcelain pot.</i>

01:31.240 --> 01:33.542
<i>Inside is a key to my locker
at the gym in Montburry.</i>

01:33.544 --> 01:35.463
<i>Everything is in there..."</i>

01:36.270 --> 01:38.382
It's "The Origin of Evil."

01:39.496 --> 01:41.452
It's Harry's
original manuscript.

01:41.454 --> 01:43.027
<i>"...Burn it all.</i>

01:43.029 --> 01:44.948
