Hey.

03:05.013 --> 03:05.971
Hey.

03:05.973 --> 03:07.353
Did you burn everything?

03:07.355 --> 03:08.581
And the manuscript?

03:08.583 --> 03:11.193
Yes, I did exactly
what you told me.

03:11.195 --> 03:13.115
Thank you.

03:14.536 --> 03:16.609
Why was that box
in your gym locker?

03:19.643 --> 03:21.446
I was afraid someone
else might find it,

03:21.448 --> 03:23.289
so I just... panicked.

03:23.291 --> 03:25.209
I thought it would be
safe somewhere else.

03:25.211 --> 03:27.052
You thought it would be safe?

03:27.054 --> 03:30.508
Mm, just makes you
look guilty, that's all.

03:30.510 --> 03:32.083
Do you think
I'm guilty, Marcus?

03:32.085 --> 03:33.849
No, Harry.
I don't.

03:33.851 --> 03:36.575
I loved her, Marcus,
but it was innocent.

03:36.577 --> 03:39.532
I never
crossed that line.

03:39.534 --> 03:43.298
And I did not kill her.

03:48.327 --> 03:49.362
The, um...

03:49.364 --> 03:52.857
the manuscript
was "The Origin of Evil."

03:52.859 --> 03:54.278
The very first draft.

03:54.280 --> 03:55.084
How come
there was no title

03:55.086 --> 03:56.044
on the cover page?

03:56.046 --> 03:58.732
The title came afterwards.

03:58.734 --> 04:00.499
After... after Nola's
disappearance, you mean?

04:00.501 --> 04:01.651
Yeah, but I don't want

04:01.653 --> 04:03.225
to talk about
the manuscript.

04:03.227 --> 04:05.606
It's brought nothing
but suffering into my life.

04:05.608 --> 04:07.528
Okay.

04:08.334 --> 04:10.444
Oh, for Christ's sake.

04:10.446 --> 04:11.365
You still have that?

04:11.367 --> 04:12.633
Yeah, it's
a good luck charm.

04:12.635 --> 04:13.862
Huh.

04:13.864 --> 04:15.859
It was a gift from
the great Harry Quebert

04:15.861 --> 04:18.086
