but you need to.

04:48.501 --> 04:51.724
Well, where shall I begin?

04:51.726 --> 04:55.567
From the beginning.

04:57.332 --> 05:01.362
<i>It was an afternoon
in June, 1975.</i>

05:01.364 --> 05:03.014
<i>I'd been struggling
up to that point</i>

05:03.016 --> 05:05.280
<i>to get started on the book,</i>

05:05.282 --> 05:07.123
<i>and I looked up,</i>

05:07.125 --> 05:10.732
<i>right when the rain
started, and...</i>

05:10.734 --> 05:13.305
<i>there she was,</i>

05:13.307 --> 05:16.340
<i>just dancing,
enjoying the rain.</i>

05:18.607 --> 05:20.526
<i>I was just lost watching her.</i>

05:22.984 --> 05:25.862
<i>That was
the first time I met her.</i>

05:28.130 --> 05:29.740
She had a magical quality
about her,

05:29.742 --> 05:31.161
something...

05:31.163 --> 05:33.083
I'd never seen before.

05:34.964 --> 05:37.421
I remember asking her
what her name was,

05:37.423 --> 05:40.223
and it wasn't until...

05:40.225 --> 05:42.489
maybe a week later

05:42.491 --> 05:45.832
that I...
I ran into her in town.

05:48.328 --> 05:51.359
<i>I was in the middle
of my morning run,</i>

05:51.361 --> 05:52.933
<i>and she appeared once again.</i>

05:52.935 --> 05:54.547
Harry!

05:54.549 --> 05:56.546
Oh, hey! Hello!

06:00.654 --> 06:01.497
Hi!

06:01.499 --> 06:02.265
Guess what?

06:02.267 --> 06:03.186
Hey, Nola!

06:03.957 --> 06:04.800
Hey, hi!

06:04.802 --> 06:06.182
Guess what?

06:06.184 --> 06:07.142
What?

06:07.144 --> 06:08.179
I checked out
your book yesterday

06:08.181 --> 06:08.947
out of the library.

06:08.949 --> 06:09.753
Uh-huh?

06:09.755 --> 06:10.867
"The Mirror of Life"?

06:10.869 --> 06:11.981
You're the only "Q"
in Fiction,

06:11.983 --> 06:13.554
right between
Boris Pasternak

06:13.556 --> 06:14.783
and Ayn Rand.

06:14.785 --> 06:16.088
What, no, uh...

06:16.090 --> 06:18.623
Pope, no Poe,
no Proust?

06:18.625 --> 06:20.082
Well, the collection
at the Sommerdale Library

06:20.084 --> 06:21.580
isn't exactly
extensive.

06:21.582 --> 06:23.462
Ah...

06:23.464 --> 06:24.268
Isn't it exciting?

06:24.270 --> 06:26.420
Yes,
uh, very exciting.

06:27.995 --> 06:28.953
It must be wonderful

06:28.955 --> 06:30.681
