as a writer,

06:30.683 --> 06:33.868
to be told your words
are worth publishing.

06:33.870 --> 06:37.555
Like you weren't
crazy to dream.

06:37.557 --> 06:41.318
Uh, yeah, well, um...

06:41.320 --> 06:44.927
success and fame
can be gratifying,

06:44.929 --> 06:47.884
I'll admit that, but...

06:47.886 --> 06:49.573
I don't know,
all the other stuff is...

06:49.575 --> 06:51.725
like, the parties and...

06:51.727 --> 06:53.260
that stuff's
overrated.

06:53.262 --> 06:54.835
I don't believe you.

06:54.837 --> 06:56.025
That's why I came
here, you know,

06:56.027 --> 06:57.446
to get away
from it all,

06:57.448 --> 06:59.790
to find some
inspiration.

07:01.480 --> 07:03.245
Well, this is me.

07:03.247 --> 07:05.357
- I work here on Saturdays.
- Okay.

07:05.359 --> 07:07.161
You should, uh, come by.

07:07.163 --> 07:09.772
Maybe it will inspire you.

07:09.774 --> 07:10.848
Okay.

07:10.850 --> 07:12.153
And I'll sneak you
a free plate of fries.

07:13.038 --> 07:15.493
- Possibly.
- Okay.

07:15.495 --> 07:17.416
See you, Nola.

07:18.991 --> 07:20.601
<i>And then I...</i>

07:20.603 --> 07:24.403
found myself thinking
about her more and more,

07:24.405 --> 07:26.169
just consuming my thoughts.

07:26.171 --> 07:28.091
Mm-hm.

07:55.701 --> 07:57.620
Nola?

07:58.735 --> 07:59.615
Are you okay?

07:59.617 --> 08:00.845
- Yes, yes, yes...
- What happened?

08:00.847 --> 08:01.843
Yes, I'm... I'm fine!

08:03.803 --> 08:05.222
Shh... Shh!

08:05.224 --> 08:06.144
