08:17.781 --> 08:19.122
She's not gonna fire you.

08:19.124 --> 08:21.158
You're, like, the best
waitress she's got anyway.

08:21.160 --> 08:22.578
Oh, my goodness,
look at this mess.

08:23.810 --> 08:24.960
Well, it's a good thing
