sure, why not?

14:21.493 --> 14:22.489
Here, after you.

14:22.491 --> 14:25.715
Ah, thank you,
Professor.

14:25.717 --> 14:27.789
Okay, a couple rounds,

14:27.791 --> 14:28.902
