but...

14:33.935 --> 14:35.046
Yeah...

14:35.048 --> 14:36.968
Come on.

14:37.429 --> 14:38.540
This is fun.
I forgot how much fun this is.

14:38.542 --> 14:40.462
All right.

14:42.574 --> 14:43.763
Whoa!

14:44.878 --> 14:45.683
